{"tid":2415534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"祖國是香港最堅強後盾 陳肇始：首批科興疫苗運抵本港","createTime":"2021-02-20T10:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T17:37:36.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59d878be9245162cc5cb65faccebbef4b34a594d","tid":2415534,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"首批100萬劑科興疫苗昨午由北京運抵本港，公務員事務局長聶德權、食物及衞生局長陳肇始、中聯辦副主任仇鴻等人在機場停機坪「接機」。港人大多抗拒國產疫苗，聶德權和陳肇始則不忘感謝中央支持及科興積極配合，形容昨日是關鍵時刻，是本港防疫、抗疫的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n運載疫苗的國泰航空CX391航班，昨午約5時40分抵達赤鱲角機場，工作人員隨即卸載七個裝載疫苗的大型凍櫃。運送人員打開貨物倉門，儲存在專用冷凍櫃的疫苗轉移到停機坪，再由貨車送走。聶德權、陳肇始、機管局行政總裁林天福、機管局主席蘇澤光等人早10分鐘在現場等候「接機」，每人臉上都掛着笑容。"},{"pid":"317dbe01baafd88227490b991272afd91aaaafc7","tid":2415534,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每人臉上都掛着笑容"},{"pid":"d7c2cb732d30cf105be4aeb5e3e30753565c6957","tid":2415534,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"每人臉上都掛着笑容，殺熟狗頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761b02208e1d20bc1ece4e5a05b97cdd1a2516b8","tid":2415534,"uid":33174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"317dbe01baafd88227490b991272afd91aaaafc7","tid":2415534,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每人臉上都掛着笑容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"癱左咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51bca18d2948ceb2700df0760395a1c9fc4b61e","tid":2415534,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d878be9245162cc5cb65faccebbef4b34a594d","tid":2415534,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"首批100萬劑科興疫苗昨午由北京運抵本港